ary population synthesis models, the nature of\nsuper-Eddington accreting objects (e.g., ultraluminous X-ray sources), recent\nefforts to identify active galactic nucleus candidates in dwarf galaxies, and\nthe X-ray radiation fields in the early Universe during the epoch of cosmic\nheating at z > 10.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2020 19:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
