that if the daily difference between\nadmissions and discharges is minimised, i.e., a patient is admitted without\ndelay when another is discharged, the number of admitted panties would\nfluctuate less and the number of unoccupied beds would be reduced optimising\nthe Hospital service.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2020 19:45:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Nov 2020 10:35:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 2020 00:36:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2020 10:18:52 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 06:56:42 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2021 08:56:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-21"}
