proach to the low-energy Hamiltonian represents a\npowerful tool for the study of materials with complex magnetic order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Nov 2020 03:19:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Jun 2021 06:23:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 21 Aug 2021 03:41:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 02:07:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-05"}
