mpact of non-Gaussianity inducing operators on the\nnonclassical and phase properties of the displaced Fock states. In Chapter 5,\nwe have performed a comparison between to process that are used in quantum\nstate engineering to induce nonclassical features. Finally, this thesis is\nconcluded in Chapter 6, where we have summarized the findings of this thesis\nand have also described scope of the future works.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Nov 2020 12:01:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-20"}
